These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, september, april, march
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, fantasy, musical, scientific
1. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching musical movies##5
2. the person who's birthday is in september is not the person watching western movies##6
3. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
6. the person watching western movies is not the person who's birthday is in april##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | september   | march    | may    | april |
| Sport      | scientific | western | musical | fantasy |

