.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, german, polish, mexican
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, taxi, subway, tram
1. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1
2. the german is somewhere to the left of the polish##5
3. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the left of the mexican##5
4. the german is not the person driving the taxi##6
5. the person driving the tram is on the left of the polish##1
6. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
7. the mexican is on the right of the dutch##1
8. the polish is somewhere to the left of the dutch##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | german  | polish    | dutch | mexican    |
| Food       | tram | taxi | subway  | bike |

