.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, amaryllis, balloon-flower, iris
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, september, august, april
1. the person who growsiris is not the person who's birthday is in may##6
2. the person who's birthday is in september is not the person who growsballoon-flower##6
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person who growsamaryllis##3
4. the person who's birthday is in september is the person who growszinnia##1
5. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
6. the person who growszinnia is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | iris       | amaryllis  | zinnia  | balloon-flower |
| Job        | august | april | september | may  |

