.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, dunhill, vegafina, bolivar
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, russian, canadian, polish
1. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
2. the dunhill-smoker is somewhere to the left of the nigerian##5
3. the polish is not the dunhill-smoker##6
4. the polish is somewhere to the right of the nigerian##5
5. the canadian is on the right of the russian##1
6. the bolivar-smoker is somewhere to the left of the polish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | dunhill | vegafina | bolivar     | havana |
| Transport   | russian     | canadian    | nigerian | polish    |

