.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, indian, italian, colombian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, handball, biathlon, volleyball
1. the american is on the left of the colombian##1
2. the colombian is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##5
3. the colombian is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is handball##5
4. the indian is not the person who's sport is volleyball##6
5. the person who's sport is surfing is not the american##6
6. the italian is on the left of the indian##1
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | american        | colombian | italian | indian |
| Transport   | volleyball | surfing | handball     | biathlon   |

