.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
There 4 different types of food: orange, broccoli, lemon, lettuce
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, july, june, february
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person eating orange##1
2. the person eating lettuce is not the person who's birthday is in july##6
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far right##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##5
5. the person eating lemon is the person eating lemon##1
6. the person eating lemon is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##5
7. the person eating lemon is somewhere to the left of the person eating orange##5
8. the person eating broccoli is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##5
9. the person eating broccoli is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | broccoli | lemon    | orange  | lettuce   |
| Nationality   | june  | february | july | april |

