.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, november, april, january
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, photographer, freelancer, chef
1. the freelancer is on the left or right of the scientist##3
2. the freelancer is not the person who's birthday is in november##6
3. the person who's birthday is in february is the photographer##1
4. the scientist is on the left or right of the chef##3
5. the freelancer is on the far left##1
6. the person who's birthday is in november is the scientist##1
7. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the left of the scientist##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | january | november     | april | february |
| Music-Genre   | freelancer | scientist | chef      | photographer         |

