.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, cooking, collecting, chess
There 4 different types of food: peach, cauliflower, pineapple, peas
1. the person eating peach is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
2. the person eating peas is somewhere to the left of the person eating pineapple##5
3. the person eating peas is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
4. the person eating cauliflower is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3
6. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
7. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
8. the person who's hobby is cooking is not the person eating peas##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | cooking  | fishing        | collecting      | chess          |
| Job        | peach | cauliflower | peas | pineapple |

