.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-9::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, begonia, daffodil, balloon-flower
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, fanta, 7up, water
1. the person who growspoppy is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking fanta is not the person who growsballoon-flower##6
3. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the right of the person who growsdaffodil##5
4. the person drinking water is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
6. the person drinking water is the person who growsdaffodil##1
7. the person who growspoppy is not the person drinking water##6
8. the person who growsbegonia is somewhere to the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | poppy  | daffodil | balloon-flower    | begonia |
| Transport   | fanta | water | 7up | milk  |

