.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, german, brazilian, british
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, d&b, metal, electronic
1. the fan reggae is not the colombian##6
2. the british is on the left of the german##1
3. the fan electronic is the fan electronic##1
4. the british is on the right of the fan electronic##1
5. the brazilian is not the fan electronic##6
6. the fan d&b is not the german##6
7. the fan electronic is in an even position##4
8. the brazilian is the fan reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | brazilian | colombian        | british  | german     |
| Sport   | reggae     | electronic | d&b | metal |

