.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
House: gothic-revival, colonial, ranch-style, farmhouse
There 4 different types of food: tomato, grapes, blueberry, broccoli
1. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
2. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the left of the gothic-revival house##5
3. the person eating blueberry is not the ranch-style house##6
4. the colonial house is between the person eating broccoli and the ranch-style house##2
5. the ranch-style house is on the left of the colonial house##1
6. the person eating grapes is between the person eating tomato and the gothic-revival house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | ranch-style | colonial    | gothic-revival | farmhouse |
| Music-Genre   | tomato         | grapes | broccoli   | blueberry     |

