The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, indie, blues, jazz
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, september, december, july
1. the fan blues is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##5
2. the fan jazz is not the person who's birthday is in november##6
3. the person who's birthday is in september is the fan jazz##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the fan indie##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is not the fan jazz##6
6. the fan indie is not the person who's birthday is in november##6
7. the fan blues is somewhere to the left of the fan indie##5
8. the fan rock is on the left of the fan blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | rock  | blues | indie | jazz |
| Transport   | december | november     | july     | september    |

