.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-13::.
4 different games are played: poker, chess, go, snooker
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, july, august, february
1. the person playing poker is somewhere to the right of the person playing chess##5
2. the person playing chess is not the person who's birthday is in july##6
3. the person playing poker is the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the person playing go is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##5
5. the person playing poker is between the person playing chess and the person who's birthday is in september##2
6. the person playing chess is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | snooker | chess      | poker | go   |
| Movie-Genre   | july     | august | february   | september |

