The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, poppy, orchid, daisy
1. the person who growsorchid is not the owner of the lizard##6
2. the person who growsorchid is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
3. the person who growsdaisy is between the owner of the chinchilla and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
4. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
5. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3     |      4       |
| Beverage      | lizard       | guinea-pig | goat     | chinchilla     |
| Movie-Genre   | marigold | orchid       | daisy | poppy |

