.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-17::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: green, chestnut, aquamarine, fuchsia
House: colonial, gothic-revival, farmhouse, cottage
1. the cottage house is on the right of the colonial house##1
2. the person who likes green is not the gothic-revival house##6
3. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
4. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
5. the person who likes aquamarine is somewhere to the left of the colonial house##5
6. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
7. the colonial house is on the left or right of the cottage house##3
8. the person who likes fuchsia is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |       3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | fuchsia    | aquamarine | chestnut | green         |
| Sport      | gothic-revival | farmhouse | colonial          | cottage |

