.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-19::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: green, ebony, purple, grey
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, analyst, journalist, software-developer
1. the analyst is somewhere to the right of the journalist##5
2. the engineer is somewhere to the right of the analyst##5
3. the analyst is on the left of the engineer##1
4. the software-developer is not the person who likes green##6
5. the person who likes purple is between the person who likes green and the person who likes ebony##2
6. the person who likes grey is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person who likes green##1
8. the software-developer is somewhere to the right of the analyst##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | ebony | purple | green | grey |
| Pet     | journalist  | analyst      | engineer  | software-developer       |

