.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-20::.
House: townhouse, victorian, tower, gothic-revival
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, sailing, tennis, badminton
1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the victorian house##3
2. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
3. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
4. the person who's sport is basketball is not the townhouse house##6
5. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is sailing##5
6. the person who's sport is sailing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | townhouse | victorian | gothic-revival      | tower   |
| Transport   | badminton  | sailing   | tennis | basketball |

 